    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <ol>
        <li>
          <h4>Agree to terms</h4>
          <p>Buyer and seller agree to secure an order via Escrow Kenya. Seller creates the order by filling the "Start Transaction" form.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Payment</h4>
          <p>Buyer receives an invitation via email and SMS, accepts it and makes payment into escrow. Money is held in both the buyer’s and seller’s escrow account.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Delivery</h4>
          <p>Seller is notified via email and SMS to proceed with delivery and delivers the goods by the due date.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Approval</h4>
          <p>Buyer confirms that everything carried on as expected by approving the order in their escrow account dashboard.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4>Escrow Release</h4>
          <p>Funds are removed from the buyer’s escrow account and made available for withdrawal in the seller’s account.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>

